(
    Basic control flow tests.
)

If true is true
    Say "if, no else"

If false is true
    Say "FAILED: if with else"
Else
    Say "if with else"

Put 0 into X
While X is not 3
    Say "While loop"
    Say X
    Build X up

Put 0 into X
Until X is 3
    Say "Until loop"
    Say X
    Build X up

(Break before loop start)
Put 0 into X
Until X is 3
    Say "Early loop exit with unreachable"
    Break
    Until X is 3
        Build X up
    (End inner loop)
(End outer loop)
